{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My-- our next step was my mother's laundry woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother's laundry woman, who was a Ukrainian, wanted to give her sanctuary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you couldn't expect, the very few people who are prepared to do it, to give sanctuary to two people, to doubly endanger themselves.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother told me, unless we find a place for you, I am not going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Consequently one night, we decided we would walk during the curfew and Mother would wait for me at the house of another friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There's a long story with this friend, but I'll try and, and shorten it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This girl lived in Luck, but she went to school in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] several years in a sanatorium for TB.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all the girls in our class were frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, there was a stigma attached to people like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we became-- she was wonderful girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we became great friends, and she took me in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I signaled to my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she went to her washer lady, who I knew where she lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I stayed overnight at Christina's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I want to say Christina was nearly four years older than I, because-- having been in the sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she was sent to Lwow to school because she had an aristocratic aunt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were in, in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were of-- we're as different as, as, as [INAUDIBLE] from one another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But we were attached.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was actually-- I was her [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] medium for distributing love letters to her boyfriends and getting them back, so-- but there's a little childish, naive sort of connection out of it.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
